        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Samuel 17:17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". But then he was to bring word to David.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
