        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "a valiant man",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Perhaps rather, a ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "worthy man",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The same word, which is often translated by ‘valour,’ ‘wealth,’ ‘might,’ is also used of any special excellence. Thus ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Proverbs 12:4",
